# Cursor Mode Routing

Pick the correct Cursor mode before editing. Full router: [`docs/CURSOR_MODES.md`](../../docs/CURSOR_MODES.md).

- **Ask** — read-only exploration; no file edits
- **Plan** — non-trivial work; include `### Critique`; get approval before coding
- **Agent** — approved execution, `[AGENT]` BUILD_PLAN rows, gate runs
- **Debug** — evidence-first triage (smoke output, KB lookup); not sprint doc edits

**Trivial vs non-trivial:** see rubric in `docs/CURSOR_MODES.md`. Uncertain → Plan.

**Transitions:** scope creep → Plan; root cause found → Agent; 3-strike → Debug then escalate.

Do not debug in Plan Mode. Do not edit in Ask Mode.
